item.title: About
item.description: Mission We care about the mental health of engineering students and aim at fostering a sense of community, engaging in fun stress-relieving events, and forming friendships to help people get through their time at Cal successfully. We are here to help people build talents, hone skills and support each other. Engineering Wellness Board Gloria Tumushabe President Alex Mutwiri Vice President Christopher Justin Gonzalez Secretary Julia Hessick Social Platforms Manager Leslie Martinez Outreach Manager Lavanya Vijayan Treasurer
